reviewText: Not well designed for Seniors. A waste of money.
NOT EXCIITING, BORING -MAKE YOU WANT TO FALL ASLEEP. THOSE GUY'S SHOULD BE BANED FROM MAKING ANOTHER DVD.. NO  INSENTIENT. YOU WILL NOT STAY FIT & FEEL YOUNGER, MORE LIKELY GO BACK TOBED.
Waste of money...was not at all what I expected.  I'm glad it was inexpensive...not worth returning.

This video packing is misleading, it states "Senior" and has a picture of a older person, however, the workouts are with Jon and another young man using some devices most senior would not use. Although some of the workout steps are slow, it's dual, there's no nice or lively music. They should have offered a preview before purchase. I would not recommend this product. I wish I could get my money back.

The product is just great. It has done wonders for my father who is now old was finding it hard to exercise. Now we are exercising together and let me tell you that I am no longer worried that my father will harm himself during exercise, thanks to this wonderful DVD.

This is a great way to workout. They give very detailed instructions and explanations for each exercise. They also make sure to emphasize the importance of staying hydrated, and to do what is reasonable for your range of motion. This is a great way for beginners and those who haven't exercised for a while to get back in the game and start to see results.
